  "text": "Recently, search and optimal foraging of bacteria have been used for solving optimization problems. To perform social foraging, an animal needs communication capabilities and over a period of time it gains advantages that can exploit the sensing capabilities of the group. This helps the group to predate on a larger prey, or alternatively, individuals could obtain better protection from predators while in a group [CITATION_1] .",
